name: DrugReceipts: DRx Kill Team Stabbi Collection

metadata.description:
The DRx Kill Team Stabbi T-shirt comes to life with DRx-perience augmented reality (AR) animation and is designed to be interoperable across multiple avatar collections. Additionally, this special wearable comes with a DRx Prescription that can be filled in the Drug Store (drx.store) for a real-life, physical version of the snapback hat. The DRx Prescriptions are size and color specific. Make sure you have the prescription you want.

Expiration Date

October 31, 2023

You must claim your physical wearable by the expiration date. You will not be able to fill your DRx Prescription after October 31, 2023 at 11:59 PM CT. Your digital wearables will not be affected.

Claim your physical merch in the Drug Store. https://drx.store

Get more info about how to claim at: drugreceipts.com/killerinfo
